abstract: There are, of course, here, as at every watering-place, a number of broken down belles, whose efforts to convince the world that they are not cracked, are truly ridiculous and absurd. abstract: The sale takes place in a large room of a building called the Calcutta Exchange. This, be it remarked, corresponds in no degree with edifices bearing a similar designation in Europe.
